{"tid":1719722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大學全部不守 切勿重蹈雨革覆轍","createTime":"2019-11-14T07:07:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T08:03:49.000Z","uid":117344,"like":16,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9ca83f6414791c5f659ff46ff04d69ea64cdf9f6","tid":1719722,"uid":117344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:07:26.000Z","msg":"大學附近係有重要嘅路，黎明行動中有價值<br />\n但係真係有必要去日日夜夜守住，五個月學唔識be water﹖<br />\n暴大個日要守，係因為黑警真係強攻<br />\n其他u做完任務好走啦<br />\n無目標嘅守無意思，守嚟搏俾狗咬﹖<br />\n有文具就要守﹖文具唔識郁﹖<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">長守結果被攻入，將損失大量手足</span></strong></span><br />\n請勿被無謂情意結、文具、據點蓋過理智<br />\n<br />\n最後 不分化 不割蓆"},{"pid":"38d7ce96e73b981d780491ee01fc60f02b0d2039","tid":1719722,"uid":117344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:08:56.000Z","msg":"唔係叫係俾人攻都唔守住<br />\n但係唔係長期留守"},{"pid":"431617c7b4f0a5166271c67e87ed2fbb6fb5af04","tid":1719722,"uid":117344,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:09:38.000Z","msg":"吸取雨革教訓"},{"pid":"c6e8726066a27d8cb10715984076e5eecb07bc09","tid":1719722,"uid":24443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"431617c7b4f0a5166271c67e87ed2fbb6fb5af04","tid":1719722,"uid":117344,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:09:38.000Z","msg":"吸取雨革教訓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:10:14.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"2fdc6e6f27c5ab755c4ef77ab1b1758c50eafbd6","tid":1719722,"uid":306434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:10:25.000Z","msg":"爆玻璃同週圍噴字、爆canteen，中大就快被人溶左"},{"pid":"09d04322454e56e5e1d507741e5ab273587012b8","tid":1719722,"uid":305536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:10:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">唔好</span><br />\n<br />\n夜晚打黨鐵<br />\n上水, 粉嶺咁成功停左火車係因為火攻車箱, 水攻閘機<br />\n<br />\n朝早公路<br />\n守cu, poly, 兩間佔左其中最重要公路<br />\n其他放棄, 唔夠人"},{"pid":"40db7f97577e57697910cefa896ab03e8b1fbb5a","tid":1719